{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_11_03",
  "title": "川咲さくら 3話 ドキドキしてる？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――CM撮影当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—CM Shoot Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます、{user}さん！\nどうですか、この衣装？　似合ってますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ {user}-san!\nHow is this outfit? Does it suit me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.1507681125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、とても似合っているぞ\nもうすぐ撮影本番だが、そっちも大丈夫そうだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it suits you very well.\nThe shoot’s about to start‚ but you seem ready too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.4400001049
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　あのアドバイスのおかげで\n告白のイメージはバッチリ掴むことが出来ました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! Thanks to that advice‚\nI’ve got a perfect image of the confession now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.3904304664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "私にとっての青春……アイドル活動において\n絶対に欠かせない人を考えることにしたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My youth… within my idol activities‚\nI decided to think about someone absolutely indispensable to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "それで何度か練習して、サニピのみんなに\n見てもらいましたけど、すっごく好評でした！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I practiced a few times and had everyone in\nSunny Peace watch‚ and it was received really well!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.1266628106
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "だから見ていて下さい、{user}さん！\nこの場にいる全員を、ドキドキさせてみせます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So please watch‚ {user}-san!\nI’ll make everyone here feel their hearts pounding!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.232921362
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.232921362
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい、突然呼び出しちゃって\nでも、あなたにどうしても伝えたいことがあるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry for calling you out so suddenly.\nBut there’s something I absolutely have to tell you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "いきなりこんなことを言われても困らせちゃうかも\nしれません……でも、どうしても伝えたくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know this might confuse you‚\nbut I really wanted to say it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.6943042915
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "その……これ、チョコレート！\n受け取って、もらえませんか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… here—chocolate!\nWould you take it…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.9936008613
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "義理とかじゃないです！　これは……その……\n本命チョコ、なんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not friendship chocolate! This is… um…\nmy true-feelings chocolate…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.1383170287
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "実は、私……あなたのことが、好きなんです\n私と、付き合ってもらえませんか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually… I… like you.\nWould you go out with me…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――CM撮影後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—After the CM Shoot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.8378622214,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1762.1377785999925,
          "startTime": 108.6
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1266.6605630000022,
          "startTime": 108.1045227844
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.0711894511
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です。{user}さん！\nどうでしたか、私の告白！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work‚ {user}-san!\nHow was my confession!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.2666580202,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.4079762936
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "凄く自然に演じることが出来て\n監督やスタッフのみなさんが凄く褒めてくれましたよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was able to act really naturally‚\nand the director and staff praised me so much!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.1999913535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.3440023583
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "練習の時と比べると見違えたよ。これなら\n今度のイベントでもドキドキしてくれると思うぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were completely different from practice. At this rate‚\nI think you’ll get everyone’s hearts pounding at the next event.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.2666580202,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ……そうですか～？\nそう言ってもらえると練習した甲斐がありました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe… really~?\nHearing that makes all the practice worth it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.8666580202,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.3206862293
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それで、さっきは聞きそびれたが\n誰をイメージして演技をしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ I forgot to ask earlier—\nwho did you imagine while acting?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.4999913535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.0141741915
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん\n{user}さんをイメージしました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course—\nI imagined you‚ {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.0999913535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.7077362858
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃんとも話したんですけど、私達は今この瞬間\n――サニーピースでいる今こそが青春なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I talked with Shizuku-chan too‚ and we realized that right now—\nthis moment of being Sunny Peace is our youth.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.0333246869,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.69785018
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "そんな青春の中を、隣で一緒に走ってくれる。一緒に\n頑張ってくれる人って素敵だな、って思ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Someone who runs alongside me through that youth‚\nsomeone who works hard together—I thought that was wonderful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.0999913535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 166.2569389505
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "お、俺を……！？　それは、その……参ったな\nさすがにそれは予想していなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "M-me…!? That’s… well… unexpected.\nI really didn’t expect that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.9333246869,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 176.5419904553
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ。{user}さんに\nずっと一緒にいてほしいって気持ちを込めたんですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe. I put all my feelings\nof wanting you to stay with me forever into it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.0333246869,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "これからも{user}さんと\n二人で青春を過ごしたいですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From now on too‚ with you‚ {user}-san‚\nI want us to spend our youth together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.3872811798,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
