    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03-skr019.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、練習してる時に気付いたんですけど\n告白の練習は、文化祭の準備みたいで楽しかったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ while we were practicing‚\npracticing confessions felt like preparing for a school festival—it was fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.4666580202,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03-skr020.m4a",
      "text": "こうやって一緒に同じことをする中で心が通じて\nお互いを好きになっちゃったりするのかもですね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Doing the same things together like this‚ our hearts connect‚\nand maybe that’s how people end up liking each other!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.9333318076,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 206.1627435212
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "役に立てたようで何よりだ。ただ……\nそういうことはあんまりよそでは言わないようにな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m glad I could help. Just…\ndon’t go saying things like that too openly‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 210.466665141,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 214.5900446737
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03-skr021.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ！？　私、何かおかしなことを\n言ってましたか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehh!? Did I say\nsomething strange?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.7333318076,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 219.4531967008
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
