      "text": "いや、俺もさくらのことは大切に思ってるし\nそこは安心してくれ。ただ、誤解されそうでな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I care about you too‚ Sakura‚\nso don’t worry—but it could be misunderstood…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223.066665141,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_03-skr022.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました！　でも、{user}さんと\n思い合えてるみたいだなんて、嬉しいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand! Still‚ it makes me happy\nto feel like we care about each other!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 232.966665141,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
