      "text": "それはそれで、他のメンバーが聞くと俺とさくらが\nいい雰囲気だったように騒がれかねないけどな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even so‚ if the other members hear it‚\nthey might start making a fuss‚ saying we looked pretty close.",
        "id": ""
